  "implementation_notes": [
    "Checked=False + Indeterminate=True is architecturally invalid and not in manifest. Do not render this combination.",
    "Hovered and Pressed states have identical Figma CSS to Default. Interaction feedback must be added via CSS :hover/:active and missing hover/pressed tokens.",
    "Focus ring uses mix-blend-mode: multiply and is positioned absolutely at -4px offset from all edges.",
    "The indeterminate property must be set via JavaScript (input.indeterminate = true) — it cannot be set in HTML.",
    "Style axis only affects the selected/indeterminate background color. All other tokens are shared.",
    "Variant count in this reference is representative. Full matrix = 3 check-states × 6 states × 3 sizes × 2 styles = 108."
  ]
